quests.desc: Get ready to pick stuff up and put it in places, because you've just entered TextWorld! First off, if it's not too much trouble, I need you to attempt to go east. And then, take a trip east. And then, try to take a trip north. And then, assure that the locker within the chamber is opened. And then, recover the key from the locker. And then, check that the chest is unlocked with the key. And then, ensure that the chest within the chamber is open. After that, recover the burger from the chest. And then, try to take a trip south. Once you succeed at that, eat the burger. And if you do that, you're the winner!
